              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The Ne-26 beam was produced by the ISOL technique",
                "and accelerated to 9.7A MeV by the CIME cyclotron at",
                "the SPIRAL facility.A S-36 primary beam at 77.5A*MeV",
                "was fragmented and stopped in a thick carbon target."
              ]
            }
          ],
