                "IOCH"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "To identify Ne-27 beam-like ejectiles in the focal",
                "plane of VAMOS, was used combinations of following",
                "parameters:",
                " -the time of flight(TOF) between a microchannel plate",
                "device before the target and the plastic scintillator",
                "VAMOS,",
                " -the energy loss delta-E in the ionization chamber of",
                "VAMOS,",
                " -the horizontal position X on the focal plane of",
                "VAMOS measured by two drift chambers."
              ]
            }
          ],
